b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":858,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding Endeavors Issue and Version Update [Update]","message":"<div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572923700\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>The automatic update for version Version 1.13.1 was applied at approximately <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572922800\\"><\/span>. In addition, we have finished applying fixes for this issue&#39;s underlying causes.<br><br>As a token of our appreciation, the following item has been sent to players who started playing before <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572922800\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbTenfold Summon Voucher x1<\/div><div>This gift can be claimed from your goodie box for up to seven days after logging in. If the gift isn&rsquo;t retrieved within seven days, it will be lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Update <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572595800\\"><\/span>]<br><\/strong><\/span>Version 1.13.1 has been released at approximately <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572577200\\"><\/span>. It includes fixes for this issue&#39;s underlying causes, and for the endeavors history page not displaying following the previous temporary fix.<br>Notes:It may take time for the store to reflect the updated information.<br><br>The fixes will only be applied after the automatic update planned at approximately <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572922800\\"><\/span>.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Update <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572501600\\"><\/span>]<br><\/strong><\/span>Following the above issue, we will send players the rewards that they couldn&#39;t obtain even though they had cleared the associated endeavors.<br><br>\\u25a0Eligible Players<br>All players who match the following conditions are eligible:<br>1) Cleared the Standard Daily Endeavors between <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572156000\\"><\/span> and <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572242399\\"><\/span> but didn&#39;t claim their associated rewards before <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572328799\\"><\/span>.<br>2) Cleared the Trick or Treasure! endeavors between <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572242400\\"><\/span> and <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572328799\\"><\/span>, and claimed all their associated rewards.<br>3) Updated the game to version 1.13.0 before <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572328799\\"><\/span>.<br><br>Eligible players can claim these rewards from their goodie boxes for up to 7 days after reception.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(44, 130, 201);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572347100\\"><\/span>]<br><\/strong><\/span>We have made a temporary fix for this issue in the data update applied at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572346800\\"><\/span>.<br>Following this, the History page of the Endeavors menu will not be accessible for the time being.<br><br>We plan to fix the endeavor history&#39;s accessibility and the underlying cause of this issue in a future update.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<br><br><\/div><hr><div>We have confirmed that the following issue regarding endeavors is occurring in v1.13.0.<br><br>\\u25a0Details of the issue<br>When clearing all the endeavors in the top part of the Daily and Special tabs of the endeavor menu, the other endeavors of these tabs will not display anymore, and their rewards will be impossible to claim.<br><br>Example: Clearing all the endeavors in the Trick or Treasure! tab and claiming all the associated rewards will make the Standard Daily Endeavors disappear.<br>This will also happen if updating the game to v1.13.0 after clearing the event endeavors and claiming their rewards.<br><br>\\u25a0How to avoid this issue<br>Please clear any endeavor that is not in the top part of the Daily or Special tabs, and claim its reward before clearing the endeavors in the top part of these tabs.<br><br>As of yet, there is no known way to fix this issue if it has already happened.<br><br>We are currently investigating this issue. Any further updates will be posted in this notice.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1572336600,"prev_article_id":"804","next_article_id":"859","image_path":"","update_time":1572923682}}}'